screen_desc: The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface with the title "Plan your ride." There is an option to select the pickup time, currently set to "Pickup now." Below that, there are fields to enter the pickup location and destination ("Where to?"). Additional options include "Search in a different city," "Set location on map," and "Saved places." The interface also includes a back arrow in the top left corner and various icons at the bottom of the screen.
